he breaks with a shoulder plate missing. With little energy he transforms 
into beast and grabs Iron Raptor's leg with his massive claw and throws it 
out from under her.
Rampage: you..... will...... never..... defeat.... me....
Rampage barely holds on without going into stasis lock
